### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Send Email Notification
POST http://localhost:3000/send-notification
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "email",
  "recipient": "john.doe@example.com",
  "subject": "Welcome to Our Platform!",
  "body": "Thank you for signing up. We're excited to have you!"
}

### Send SMS Notification
POST http://localhost:3000/send-notification
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "sms",
  "recipient": "+1234567890",
  "body": "Your verification code is: 123456"
}

### Send Push Notification
POST http://localhost:3000/send-notification
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "push",
  "recipient": "device_token_xyz",
  "subject": "New Message",
  "body": "You have a new message from Jane"
}

### Send Bulk Notifications
POST http://localhost:3000/send-bulk-notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notifications": [
    {
      "type": "email",
      "recipient": "user1@example.com",
      "subject": "Bulk Email 1",
      "body": "This is bulk email 1"
    },
    {
      "type": "sms",
      "recipient": "+1111111111",
      "body": "Bulk SMS message"
    },
    {
      "type": "push",
      "recipient": "device_1",
      "subject": "Bulk Push",
      "body": "This is a bulk push notification"
    }
  ]
}

